{"tid":213628,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【金仔出手】再有一名韓裔美國公民平壤被拘 救濟北韓人民都唔畀？","createTime":"2017-04-23T09:09:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-23T10:43:35.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6773dba1467274e767b75694c9044a04329e2fb9","tid":213628,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T09:09:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170423/large/1492927063_9a24.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170423%2Flarge%2F1492927063_9a24.jpg&h=7c72fe39&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n韓聯社引述消息報道，北韓上周五拘捕一名50多歲的韓裔美國人，他是一名大學前教授，成為最近第3名被平壤拘留的美國公民。<br />\n<br />\n被扣留的美國人姓金，是延邊大學科學技術學院前教授，他上周五準備由平壤機場離境時被捕。據報他一直有從事支援及救助北韓人民的活動，他在北韓逗留的一個月期間，就是討論相關援助方案，暫時未知他被捕的原因。<br />\n首爾的國際北韓問題研究中心總監安江日（Ahn Chan-il，音譯）認為，目前美國及北韓關係惡化，平壤似乎有意利用金教授作為談判籌碼。<br />\n他是近年被北韓拘捕的第3名美國人，韓裔美國人金東哲（Kim Dong Chul，音譯）以及美國學生瓦姆比爾（Otto Warmbier），去年被最高法院判顛覆北韓社會體制、以及間諜活動罪名成立，分別判處10年及15年勞改。<br />\n韓聯社/《蘋果》資料室  <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170423/56602021\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170423%2F56602021&d=aFheyUS8Hi5o9a%2F4VMBAnQEk2Noh57F05xbgvjQdsX8%3D&h=4094fcca\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170423%2F56602021&h=d760a60b\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170423/56602021</a>"},{"pid":"fa1f3a286a46b927284ab507ac0c2d0a89eda456","tid":213628,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T09:57:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ac9a482f4c53de87bf2bf8bdedcdbd4d39841da","tid":213628,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T10:19:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0051710fa65523425ed910b41ce8660b481f9555","tid":213628,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T10:43:35.000Z","msg":"左膠抵撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n垃圾有咩好救"}]}